About us

About us
.
Himalaya Television, named after the mighty Himalayas, is a channel that has a vision beyond the conventional vogues of broadcasting. Our ambition is not solely to show but also to raise awareness of human issues and embrace the heterogeneous needs of a multicultural society. Himalaya Television reaches out to all the people of Nepal from the plains of the Terai to the high lands of the Himalayas and to those struggling for their livelihood abroad. Himalaya Television Network (HTV), one of the top premium infotainment Satellite Television channels in the Nation started in the year 2010 and has been successfully able to create its identity in a short span of time.
